item.backmath.queen_sophie_battle_info.d: I recommend you to read the Patchouli page about Queen Sophie, but if you don't have the mod installed, here's the guide. Minimum recommended gear: fully enchanted netherite armor, gear and bow, A shield and a few Aljame Teacups and regular food and finally, a 48x48 square or round area should do, or you can just do it in the wild, but you might run the risk of it despawning her. And that's it.
item.backmath.enchanted_golden_apple_jam: Bread with Enchanted Golden Apple Jam
item.backmath.pine_jelly.desc: §7"Edible item that gives you 5 golden hearts and it's not that easy to obtain :D" - Original idea quote by Sophie
item.backmath.pink_gum_frying_pan.desc: §7"This pan is entirely light pink, and when you hit a mob, the mob gets stuck in the pan (gets Slowness IV (4)) and takes constant damage (per tick)." - Original idea quote by Sophie.
item.backmath.bread_with_pao.desc: §7"Bread with bread, so good." - Original idea quote by Sophie
item.backmath.patience_tea.quote: "Patience tea leaves you out of patience and if you get close to a mob you K1LL them." - Original idea quote by Sophie
item.backmath.patience_tea.desc: Gives you 30 seconds of Patience effect, which deals the same damage as the Harming effect but at twice per second. Can be given to any mob by (shift) right-clicking.
item.backmath.peace_tea.quote: "You get so blessed that if you get close to an animal, it DIE- just kidding, it gets so blessed that it gets all the effects and never dies EVER AGAIN." - Original idea quote by Sophie
item.backmath.peace_tea.desc: Gives you all beneficial effects from vanilla and Mood effect for 5 minutes. Can be given to any mob by (shift) right-clicking.
item.backmath.disgust_tea.quote: "When you drink this tea you get disgusted/nausea from everything you eat." - Original idea quote by Sophie
item.backmath.disgust_tea.desc: Gives you Disgust effect for 30 seconds, which is supposed to give Nausea effect for 15 seconds after you eat anything. Can be given to any mob by (shift) right-clicking.
item.backmath.mood_tea.quote: "The Mood tea works as follows. It acts just like Minecraft milk. It takes away bad effects: poison, weakness." - Original idea quote by Sophie
item.backmath.mood_tea.desc: Gives you Mood effect for 5 minutes, which removes any neutral or harmful effect from you twice per second. Can be given to any mob by (shift) right-clicking.
item.backmath.mood_tea.bug: Though there's a bug that when the effect removes effects that apply attributes to the player, such as Slowness or Weakness, the effect itself is removed but not the attribute/effect on the player, so you stay slow/weak without the effect applied. Only way to remove is to remove the Mood effect, give yourself Weakness or Slowness and then drink milk or wait for it to end.
